            <name>Welcome_Text_0</name>
            <fieldText>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;We’re excited to be hiring Student Experience Team Members for our client Unite Students. &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Opportunities are available across their student accommodations in Aberdeen, Birmingham, Bristol, Durham, Edinburgh, Gillingham, Glasgow, Leeds, Liverpool, London, Loughborough, Manchester, Newcastle, Nottingham and Sheffield. These roles are permanent with the option to work either day shifts between the hours of 7am and 11pm or night shifts between the hours of 10pm and 7am.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;We’d love to know more about your experience, skills and availability to make sure this is the right role for you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;This shouldn’t take more than a couple of minutes – click below to start your journey.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</fieldText>
